Package user.attendee

Class AttendeePresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Presenter
      • user.UserPresenter
        • user.attendee.AttendeePresenter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OrganizerPresenter, SpeakerPresenter
    public class AttendeePresenter
extends UserPresenter
    This class is a Presenter Class with specific functionality for Attendee Controllers. It handles asking for user input and printing any error messages.
